<L>__{exterior mao's office night}
<A>__{outside this building, a black car is waiting. it is bitterly cold. mao wearing no hat, no coat, and coughing opens the door for the boy. the dalai lama shakes the man's hand.}
<C>__{mao tse tung}
<D>__{take care of your health.}
<A>__{tenzin gyatso gets into the car and mao slams the door.}
<L>__{interior car night}
<A>__{as the car drives away, tenzin gyatso turns to see the chairman, still standing in the cold, still waving goodbye. then, tenzin gyatso looks straight ahead and says:}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{he will betray us.}
<A>__{the view pulls back. the lord chamberlain sits beside the young man.}
<C>__{lord chambepiain}
<D>__{did you ever doubt it?}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{i had relinquished doubt.}
